---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Hayaan Dangra"
  description="High school senior at Alliance Academy exploring cyber security, healthcare tech, and math visualizations."
>
  <section class="hero section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bio section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <p>
          I'm Hayaan Dangra, a high school senior at Alliance Academy in Georgia.
        </p>
        <p>
          I build things on the internet — websites, tools, visualizations — and I've been doing it since I realized that the best way to learn something is to make something with it.
        </p>
        <p>
          My biggest project so far: I built the website for my family's food business (Elote King), optimized the SEO, and helped sell out 2 events from a landing page I coded.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="current-work section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What I'm Into Right Now</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Math Explorations</h3>
          <p>GHP semifinalist, building interactive visualizations to explore chaos theory, prime patterns, and wave mathematics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Cyber Security</h3>
          <p>School pathway at Alliance Academy — learning defense strategies, ethical hacking, and network security.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Healthcare Technology</h3>
          <p>School pathway at Alliance Academy — exploring the intersection of technology and healthcare delivery.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Teaching Kids to Code</h3>
          <p>At Creative Labs Learning Center — helping the next generation learn to build and create.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stack section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>My Stack</h2>
      <div class="content">
        <ul class="stack-list">
          <li>HTML, CSS, JavaScript</li>
          <li>Astro (static sites)</li>
          <li>SEO & analytics</li>
          <li>AI-assisted development (vibe coding)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="next section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What's Next</h2>
      <div class="content">
        <p>
          I'm looking for the kind of challenge where I can go deeper — whether that's GHP this summer, a cyber security project, or the next business problem that needs a website.
        </p>
        <p>
          <!-- TODO: Replace # with Hayaan's actual profile URLs when created -->
          If you want to follow what I'm building, find me on <a href="#">X</a> or <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background-color: var(--light-gray);
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .bio,
  .stack,
  .next {
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .current-work {
    background-color: var(--light-gray);
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .content p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }
  }

  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .card {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .stack-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .stack-list li {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    position: relative;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }

  .stack-list li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .next .content {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .next a {
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
